snippet.title: Road To Siren Hills Release Trailer
snippet.description:
#silenthill #godot #sirenhead

Your car has died in the middle of nowhere.
The only thing you see is darkness and a flashlight lying on the grass.
Your only option is to go on foot, but where will the journey lead you to?

Road To Siren Hills is an atmospheric, psychological horror game inspired by the Silent Hill series.

Have fun and get scared.

Check out the extended version here:
https://voxelvoid.itch.io/road-to-siren-hills-dark-journey

Original Siren Head design by Trevor Henderson
